{"name":"Short Circuit","permission":{"default":0,"qJl17WpEHiovQQBC":3},"type":"sleight","data":{"description":"<p>You force the target&rsquo;s synapses to misfire. This functions like a shock attack ▶219; the target loses neuromuscular control, falls down, and is incapacitated for 1 action turn (+2 turns per superior success) and stunned for 3 minutes.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 285","duration":"instant","infectionMod":6,"sleightType":"gamma","action":"complex","timeframe":0,"effectsToSelf":[],"effectsToTarget":[{"type":"misc","unique":"","description":"Target’s synapses misfire, they are incapacitated for 1 turn and stunned for 3 minutes.","id":"7f819i0pqb"}],"scaleEffectsOnSuperior":false,"attack":{"useMentalArmor":false,"attackTraits":["shock"],"damageFormula":"","damageType":"mental","notes":""},"heal":{"formula":"","healthType":"mental"},"mentalArmor":{"apply":false,"divisor":3,"formula":"1d6"},"status":{"sustaining":false,"pushDuration":0,"pushed":false,"pushStartTime":0,"sustainingOn":[]}},"flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"1E0khF9kWJvch40O"}
{"name":"Burst of Adrenaline","permission":{"default":0,"qJl17WpEHiovQQBC":3},"type":"sleight","data":{"description":"<p>You revive the target with a rush of endorphins and energy. They receive +1 Vigor pool for WIL &divide; 5 minutes. A target may only benefit from one burst of adrenaline at a time.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 283","duration":"minutes","infectionMod":6,"sleightType":"gamma","action":"complex","timeframe":0,"effectsToSelf":[],"effectsToTarget":[{"type":"pool","pool":"vigor","modifier":1,"usabilityModification":"","id":"zwr1xjq98k"}],"scaleEffectsOnSuperior":false,"attack":{"useMentalArmor":false,"attackTraits":[],"damageFormula":"","damageType":"mental","notes":""},"heal":{"formula":"","healthType":"mental"},"mentalArmor":{"apply":false,"divisor":3,"formula":"1d6"},"status":{"sustaining":false,"pushDuration":0,"pushed":false,"pushStartTime":0,"sustainingOn":[]}},"flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"9whYcVRCFR8VQ2rZ"}
{"name":"Mindlink","permission":{"default":0,"qJl17WpEHiovQQBC":3},"type":"sleight","data":{"description":"<p>You establish two-way mental communication with the target. If mindlinked with more than one target simultaneously, you may act as a telepathic server so that everyone mindlinked with you can also telepathically communicate with each other (though you will overhear everything). Language is still a factor in mindlinked communications, but this barrier may be overcome by transmitting sounds, images, emotions, and other sensations.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 285","duration":"sustained","infectionMod":2,"sleightType":"gamma","action":"quick","timeframe":0,"effectsToSelf":[{"type":"misc","unique":"","description":"Telepathy.","id":"tyd1xo1u8l"}],"effectsToTarget":[{"type":"misc","unique":"","description":"Telepathy.","id":"n9thcggqa8"}],"scaleEffectsOnSuperior":false,"attack":{"useMentalArmor":false,"attackTraits":[],"damageFormula":"","damageType":"mental","notes":""},"heal":{"formula":"","healthType":"mental"},"mentalArmor":{"apply":false,"divisor":3,"formula":"1d6"},"status":{"sustaining":false,"pushDuration":0,"pushed":false,"pushStartTime":0,"sustainingOn":[]}},"flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"AVgT3kOqn7oJSDJA"}
{"name":"Illusion","permission":{"default":0,"qJl17WpEHiovQQBC":3},"type":"sleight","data":{"description":"<p>You craft an illusion and inflict it upon the target. The illusion can range from a simple single-sense impression to a completely immersive false reality and can override actual sensory input. The illusion cannot directly harm the target, but it can provoke reactions that are dangerous or even fatal (i.e., tricking someone into walking off a roof ). Because the illusion is unsubstantial, it also may not stop or start movement, hold weight, provide protection, etc. If the target carefully examines the illusion or physically interacts with it, they receive an INT Check to see through it. Likewise, if the illusion in any way defies reality or inspires common-sense incredulity, or the real world interferes with the illusion (sudden loud noises, walls hidden by the illusion impede movement, etc.), the target gets an INT Check to disbelieve. Targets that succeed in their INT Check will still faintly experience the illusory input, but recognize it as unreal. No check is needed if the target has proof the illusion is false. Complex or lengthy illusions are hard to sustain; the GM may call for INT Checks or appropriate skill tests to maintain the constructed facade.</p>\n<p>Illusions require intense mental power to sustain. You may not take any complex actions while sustaining this sleight, else the illusion will falter.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 284","duration":"sustained","infectionMod":8,"sleightType":"gamma","action":"complex","timeframe":0,"effectsToSelf":[{"type":"misc","unique":"","description":"You're sustaining a full-sensory illusion on your target.","id":"su7vfd0u1n"}],"effectsToTarget":[{"type":"misc","unique":"","description":"Target experiences full-sensory illusion crafted by async.","id":"1sx1cl4o9v"}],"scaleEffectsOnSuperior":false,"attack":{"useMentalArmor":false,"attackTraits":[],"damageFormula":"","damageType":"mental","notes":""},"heal":{"formula":"","healthType":"mental"},"mentalArmor":{"apply":false,"divisor":3,"formula":"1d6"},"status":{"sustaining":false,"pushDuration":0,"pushed":false,"pushStartTime":0,"sustainingOn":[]}},"flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"Ag0V9ipW4n0DovaI"}
{"name":"Nightmare","permission":{"default":0,"qJl17WpEHiovQQBC":3},"type":"sleight","data":{"description":"<p>You bombard the target with horrific images and sensations, eroding their mental stability. You inflict 2d10 SV to the target, +1d6 per superior success. This is reduced by mental armor.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 285","duration":"instant","infectionMod":6,"sleightType":"gamma","action":"complex","timeframe":0,"effectsToSelf":[],"effectsToTarget":[{"type":"misc","unique":"","description":"Reduced by Psi armor","id":"9sism0vdxo"}],"scaleEffectsOnSuperior":false,"attack":{"useMentalArmor":true,"attackTraits":[],"damageFormula":"2d10","damageType":"mental","notes":""},"heal":{"formula":"","healthType":"mental"},"mentalArmor":{"apply":false,"divisor":3,"formula":"1d6"},"status":{"sustaining":false,"pushDuration":0,"pushed":false,"pushStartTime":0,"sustainingOn":[]}},"flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"EvCIOHj0gXpe0Zio"}
{"name":"Implant Memory","permission":{"default":0,"qJl17WpEHiovQQBC":3},"type":"sleight","data":{"description":"<p>You implant a memory of up to an hour&rsquo;s length inside the target&rsquo;s mind. This memory may be completely fabricated, based on your real memories, or a combination of the two. Implanting real memories is useful for archiving important data with an ally, providing a literal alternate perspective, or simply making a memory dump for the target to peruse. Fake memories are often fuzzy and lacking detail, but bolstering them with real memories makes them more convincing. At the GM&rsquo;s discretion, a fake memory that contradicts the target&rsquo;s other memories, is drastically out of character, or includes details that inspire skepticism may be identified as false with an INT Check. Particularly traumatic memories may inflict mental stress on the recipient when they are first experienced. Implanted memories do not overwrite real memories.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 284","duration":"instant","infectionMod":6,"sleightType":"gamma","action":"complex","timeframe":0,"effectsToSelf":[],"effectsToTarget":[{"type":"misc","unique":"","description":"Implant fake memory permanently in target.","id":"lnkbd5arso"}],"scaleEffectsOnSuperior":false,"attack":{"useMentalArmor":false,"attackTraits":[],"damageFormula":"","damageType":"mental","notes":""},"heal":{"formula":"","healthType":"mental"},"mentalArmor":{"apply":false,"divisor":3,"formula":"1d6"},"status":{"sustaining":false,"pushDuration":0,"pushed":false,"pushStartTime":0,"sustainingOn":[]}},"flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"FrxTtmEhpwEnSzKW"}
{"name":"Aphasia","permission":{"default":0,"qJl17WpEHiovQQBC":3},"type":"sleight","data":{"description":"<p>You create a temporary stroke-like effect within the target&rsquo;s brain that disrupts their speech and language centers. For WIL &divide; 5 minutes, they are incapable of speaking, communicating, reading, and understanding language.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 282","duration":"minutes","infectionMod":6,"sleightType":"gamma","action":"complex","timeframe":0,"effectsToSelf":[],"effectsToTarget":[{"type":"misc","unique":"","description":"Target cannot speak, communicate, or read.","id":"o4j5ym9lmp"}],"scaleEffectsOnSuperior":false,"attack":{"useMentalArmor":false,"attackTraits":[],"damageFormula":"","damageType":"mental","notes":""},"heal":{"formula":"","healthType":"mental"},"mentalArmor":{"apply":false,"divisor":3,"formula":"1d6"},"status":{"sustaining":false,"pushDuration":0,"pushed":false,"pushStartTime":0,"sustainingOn":[]}},"flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"Hk21h9TMkakIFug8"}
{"name":"Mimic","permission":{"default":0,"qJl17WpEHiovQQBC":3},"type":"sleight","data":{"description":"<p>You telepathically ping the target, collecting an intuitive snapshot of their personality quirks and mannerisms. You may use this imprint of the target&rsquo;s mind to your advantage when mimicking their behavior and social cues. Apply a +10 modifier to Deceive Tests to impersonate the target, +10 per superior success.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 285","duration":"instant","infectionMod":4,"sleightType":"gamma","action":"quick","timeframe":0,"effectsToSelf":[],"effectsToTarget":[{"type":"successTest","tags":[{"type":"skill","skillType":"deceive"}],"modifier":10,"toOpponent":false,"requirement":"impersonating target","id":"peunuifwpm"}],"scaleEffectsOnSuperior":true,"attack":{"useMentalArmor":false,"attackTraits":[],"damageFormula":"","damageType":"mental","notes":""},"heal":{"formula":"","healthType":"mental"},"mentalArmor":{"apply":false,"divisor":3,"formula":"1d6"},"status":{"sustaining":false,"pushDuration":0,"pushed":false,"pushStartTime":0,"sustainingOn":[]}},"flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"INUdMtkCHzx6wPNi"}
{"name":"Pain","permission":{"default":0,"qJl17WpEHiovQQBC":3},"type":"sleight","data":{"description":"<p>You activate the target&rsquo;s nerve endings and clusters, inflicting a painful burning sensation. Treat as a pain effect ▶216; the target must take their next action to flee away from the async or area at full movement.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 285","duration":"instant","infectionMod":6,"sleightType":"gamma","action":"complex","timeframe":0,"effectsToSelf":[],"effectsToTarget":[{"type":"misc","unique":"","description":"Target inflicted with pain (like an agonizer), must flee at full movement on their next action.","id":"yvlap91xj4"}],"scaleEffectsOnSuperior":false,"attack":{"useMentalArmor":false,"attackTraits":["pain"],"damageFormula":"","damageType":"mental","notes":""},"heal":{"formula":"","healthType":"mental"},"mentalArmor":{"apply":false,"divisor":3,"formula":"1d6"},"status":{"sustaining":false,"pushDuration":0,"pushed":false,"pushStartTime":0,"sustainingOn":[]}},"flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"JbnI6u9VpI44vacU"}
{"name":"Block Pain","permission":{"default":0,"qJl17WpEHiovQQBC":3},"type":"sleight","data":{"description":"<p>You impede the target&rsquo;s pain receptors. For WIL &divide; 5 minutes, the target can ignore the effects of one wound, plus one per superior success. This is cumulative with other pain editing effects, up to a maximum of 3 wound effects.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 282","duration":"minutes","infectionMod":4,"sleightType":"gamma","action":"complex","timeframe":0,"effectsToSelf":[],"effectsToTarget":[{"type":"health","health":"physical","stat":"woundsIgnored","modifier":1,"id":"69ssfd4na8"}],"scaleEffectsOnSuperior":true,"attack":{"useMentalArmor":false,"attackTraits":[],"damageFormula":"","damageType":"mental","notes":""},"heal":{"formula":"","healthType":"mental"},"mentalArmor":{"apply":false,"divisor":3,"formula":"1d6"},"status":{"sustaining":false,"pushDuration":0,"pushed":false,"pushStartTime":0,"sustainingOn":[]}},"flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"JyKyXIxljaIEpMZD"}
{"name":"Neural Hardening","permission":{"default":0,"qJl17WpEHiovQQBC":3},"type":"sleight","data":{"description":"<p>You harden the target&rsquo;s sensory input pathways and mechanisms. For WIL &divide; 5 minutes, they receive +10 to resist basilisk hacks, +10 per superior success.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 285","duration":"minutes","infectionMod":4,"sleightType":"gamma","action":"complex","timeframe":0,"effectsToSelf":[],"effectsToTarget":[{"type":"successTest","tags":[{"type":"aptitudeCheck","aptitude":"int"}],"modifier":10,"toOpponent":false,"requirement":"resisting Basilisk Hacks","id":"a6vs7o0i3o"}],"scaleEffectsOnSuperior":true,"attack":{"useMentalArmor":false,"attackTraits":[],"damageFormula":"","damageType":"mental","notes":""},"heal":{"formula":"","healthType":"mental"},"mentalArmor":{"apply":false,"divisor":3,"formula":"1d6"},"status":{"sustaining":false,"pushDuration":0,"pushed":false,"pushStartTime":0,"sustainingOn":[]}},"flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"Kq8Yo1NK5TNSFqvc"}
{"name":"Implant Skill","permission":{"default":0,"qJl17WpEHiovQQBC":3},"type":"sleight","data":{"description":"<p>You impart your expertise and implant it into the target&rsquo;s mind. The target acquires your chosen existing skill at half value for WIL &divide; 5 hours. If the target already has the skill, they use whichever value is higher. Specialization bonuses also apply. Psi skill may only be implanted if the target has the Psi trait. Recipients of skills will exercise them with the async&rsquo;s flair and mannerisms.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 284","duration":"hours","infectionMod":6,"sleightType":"gamma","action":"complex","timeframe":0,"effectsToSelf":[],"effectsToTarget":[{"type":"misc","unique":"","description":"Implant skill possessed by async in target’s mind at half value.","id":"udkr4qh6mx"}],"scaleEffectsOnSuperior":false,"attack":{"useMentalArmor":false,"attackTraits":[],"damageFormula":"","damageType":"mental","notes":""},"heal":{"formula":"","healthType":"mental"},"mentalArmor":{"apply":false,"divisor":3,"formula":"1d6"},"status":{"sustaining":false,"pushDuration":0,"pushed":false,"pushStartTime":0,"sustainingOn":[]}},"flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"L0xa93swT3uD8fQW"}
{"name":"Alter Effect","permission":{"default":0,"qJl17WpEHiovQQBC":3},"type":"sleight","data":{"description":"<p>You trigger or ease a neurochemical response within the target, either decreasing or increasing the duration of a drug, chemical, or toxin by half.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 282","duration":"instant","infectionMod":2,"sleightType":"gamma","action":"complex","timeframe":0,"effectsToSelf":[],"effectsToTarget":[{"type":"misc","unique":"","description":"Increase or reduce the duration of a drug or toxin affecting the target by half.","id":"msmfzev8z2"}],"scaleEffectsOnSuperior":false,"attack":{"useMentalArmor":false,"attackTraits":[],"damageFormula":"","damageType":"mental","notes":""},"heal":{"formula":"","healthType":"mental"},"mentalArmor":{"apply":false,"divisor":3,"formula":"1d6"},"status":{"sustaining":false,"pushDuration":0,"pushed":false,"pushStartTime":0,"sustainingOn":[]}},"flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"NL7dnuXwhM9L8Hlx"}
{"name":"Tranqulity","permission":{"default":0,"qJl17WpEHiovQQBC":3},"type":"sleight","data":{"description":"<p>You calm the target, relieving stress and anxiety. The target is relieved of the effects of an acute stress response ▶222 or triggered disorder for WIL &divide; 5 minutes. You may not use this sleight on yourself.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 285","duration":"minutes","infectionMod":4,"sleightType":"gamma","action":"complex","timeframe":0,"effectsToSelf":[],"effectsToTarget":[{"type":"misc","unique":"","description":"Target relieved from an acute stress response or triggered disorder. May not be used on self.","id":"11v2saielj"}],"scaleEffectsOnSuperior":false,"attack":{"useMentalArmor":false,"attackTraits":[],"damageFormula":"","damageType":"mental","notes":""},"heal":{"formula":"","healthType":"mental"},"mentalArmor":{"apply":false,"divisor":3,"formula":"1d6"},"status":{"sustaining":false,"pushDuration":0,"pushed":false,"pushStartTime":0,"sustainingOn":[]}},"flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"TolCS7iiRJQHhu66"}
{"name":"Static","permission":{"default":0,"qJl17WpEHiovQQBC":3},"type":"sleight","data":{"description":"<p>You generate an anti-psi jamming field, impeding the use of ranged sleights within Close range by -30. This sleight has no effect on self or Touch-range sleights.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 285","duration":"sustained","infectionMod":4,"sleightType":"gamma","action":"complex","timeframe":0,"effectsToSelf":[],"effectsToTarget":[{"type":"successTest","tags":[{"type":"skill","skillType":"psi"}],"modifier":-30,"toOpponent":false,"requirement":"using a ranged sleight in close range","id":"tz8ecjd4if"}],"scaleEffectsOnSuperior":false,"attack":{"useMentalArmor":false,"attackTraits":[],"damageFormula":"","damageType":"mental","notes":""},"heal":{"formula":"","healthType":"mental"},"mentalArmor":{"apply":false,"divisor":3,"formula":"1d6"},"status":{"sustaining":false,"pushDuration":0,"pushed":false,"pushStartTime":0,"sustainingOn":[]}},"flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"UFDflG6rxj7TZETL"}
{"name":"Browse Thoughts","permission":{"default":0,"qJl17WpEHiovQQBC":3},"type":"sleight","data":{"description":"<p>You scan the target&rsquo;s surface thoughts, gaining a general sense of what is currently running through their mind. Superior successes provide deeper detail. This is not an invasive delve into the target&rsquo;s mind for specific information like Deep Scan ▶283; instead, you simply get a read on what the target is currently thinking.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 283","duration":"sustained","infectionMod":4,"sleightType":"gamma","action":"complex","timeframe":0,"effectsToSelf":[{"type":"misc","unique":"","description":"Scan target’s surface thoughts.","id":"iszolj90pb"}],"effectsToTarget":[{"type":"misc","unique":"","description":"Your surface thoughts are being scanned.","id":"7n64almxms"}],"scaleEffectsOnSuperior":false,"attack":{"useMentalArmor":false,"attackTraits":[],"damageFormula":"","damageType":"mental","notes":""},"heal":{"formula":"","healthType":"mental"},"mentalArmor":{"apply":false,"divisor":3,"formula":"1d6"},"status":{"sustaining":false,"pushDuration":0,"pushed":false,"pushStartTime":0,"sustainingOn":[]}},"flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"Vgh6byar6bUeykHL"}
{"name":"Animal Control","permission":{"default":0,"qJl17WpEHiovQQBC":3},"type":"sleight","data":{"description":"<p>You take over the mind of a non-sapient animal. While sustained, you control the animal exactly like remotely operating a drone ▶346. You may switch between autonomous mode and jamming.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 282","duration":"sustained","infectionMod":6,"sleightType":"gamma","action":"complex","timeframe":0,"effectsToSelf":[{"type":"misc","unique":"","description":"Take over a non-sapient animal’s mind, teleoperate it like a drone.","id":"y05cjkyip5"}],"effectsToTarget":[{"type":"misc","unique":"","description":"Your body is being controlled by someone else.","id":"5kwxszhcgo"}],"scaleEffectsOnSuperior":false,"attack":{"useMentalArmor":false,"attackTraits":[],"damageFormula":"","damageType":"mental","notes":""},"heal":{"formula":"","healthType":"mental"},"mentalArmor":{"apply":false,"divisor":3,"formula":"1d6"},"status":{"sustaining":false,"pushDuration":0,"pushed":false,"pushStartTime":0,"sustainingOn":[]}},"flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"VxrUGoPHprbMyaes"}
{"name":"Block Sense","permission":{"default":0,"qJl17WpEHiovQQBC":3},"type":"sleight","data":{"description":"<p>You short-circuit and temporary disable one of the target&rsquo;s sensory cortices (your choice). For WIL &divide; 5 action turns, the target loses that type of sensory input. The senses that may be negated include sight, hearing, touch, smell, taste, hunger, balance, direction, proprioception, facial recognition, and augmented senses such as electrical sense and radiation sense. Any actions that rely on the impaired sense require a test with a minimum -30 modifier.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 282","duration":"actionTurns","infectionMod":4,"sleightType":"gamma","action":"complex","timeframe":0,"effectsToSelf":[],"effectsToTarget":[{"type":"misc","unique":"","description":"Negates one of the target’s senses (hearing, sight, smell, taste, touch).","id":"2w31xylm23"},{"type":"successTest","tags":[{"type":"action","action":"","subtype":""}],"modifier":-30,"toOpponent":false,"requirement":"relying on impaired sense","id":"narh2ylqal"}],"scaleEffectsOnSuperior":false,"attack":{"useMentalArmor":false,"attackTraits":[],"damageFormula":"","damageType":"mental","notes":""},"heal":{"formula":"","healthType":"mental"},"mentalArmor":{"apply":false,"divisor":3,"formula":"1d6"},"status":{"sustaining":false,"pushDuration":0,"pushed":false,"pushStartTime":0,"sustainingOn":[]}},"flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"WqvQjL3dgTX06CSu"}
{"name":"Ego Sense","permission":{"default":0,"qJl17WpEHiovQQBC":3},"type":"sleight","data":{"description":"<p>You detect the presence and location (rough direction from yourself) of other sentient and biological life forms (i.e., egos and animals) within Close range. Each life form makes an opposed test against your roll. You suffer modifiers for size, the same as for ranged attacks. Superior successes provide additional details: approximate size, exact distance, type of creature, etc. If the target moves during the duration (WIL &divide; 5 action turns), you will have a rough idea of their speed and bearing.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 284","duration":"actionTurns","infectionMod":2,"sleightType":"gamma","action":"complex","timeframe":0,"effectsToSelf":[],"effectsToTarget":[{"type":"misc","unique":"","description":"Detect biological life; extra info on range, size, type, etc with superior successes.","id":"06ryc23y7g"}],"scaleEffectsOnSuperior":false,"attack":{"useMentalArmor":false,"attackTraits":[],"damageFormula":"","damageType":"mental","notes":""},"heal":{"formula":"","healthType":"mental"},"mentalArmor":{"apply":false,"divisor":3,"formula":"1d6"},"status":{"sustaining":false,"pushDuration":0,"pushed":false,"pushStartTime":0,"sustainingOn":[]}},"flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"X2DkYqHlahzyonzm"}
{"name":"Psychic Stab","permission":{"default":0,"qJl17WpEHiovQQBC":3},"type":"sleight","data":{"description":"<p>You trigger dangerous neurochemical impulses and biofeedback in the target&rsquo;s brain and nervous system. You inflict 2d10 DV, +1d6 per superior success, reduced by mental armor.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 285","duration":"instant","infectionMod":6,"sleightType":"gamma","action":"complex","timeframe":0,"effectsToSelf":[],"effectsToTarget":[],"scaleEffectsOnSuperior":false,"attack":{"useMentalArmor":true,"attackTraits":[],"damageFormula":"2d10","damageType":"physical","notes":""},"heal":{"formula":"","healthType":"mental"},"mentalArmor":{"apply":false,"divisor":3,"formula":"1d6"},"status":{"sustaining":false,"pushDuration":0,"pushed":false,"pushStartTime":0,"sustainingOn":[]}},"flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"X6zZRCURQazD8rFA"}
{"name":"Empathic Scan","permission":{"default":0,"qJl17WpEHiovQQBC":3},"type":"sleight","data":{"description":"<p>You sense the target&rsquo;s emotional state for WIL &divide; 5 action turns. This provides you with a +10 modifier for social skill tests against the target, +10 per superior success. This sleight will not automatically detect deceit, but it will pick up on nervousness, doubt, anxiety, etc. and provide a bonus to Kinesics Tests against Deceive.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 284","duration":"actionTurns","infectionMod":4,"sleightType":"gamma","action":"complex","timeframe":0,"effectsToSelf":[],"effectsToTarget":[{"type":"successTest","tags":[{"type":"skillCategory","category":"social"}],"modifier":10,"toOpponent":true,"requirement":"targeted by Empathetic Scan user","id":"lmyoccednv"}],"scaleEffectsOnSuperior":true,"attack":{"useMentalArmor":false,"attackTraits":[],"damageFormula":"","damageType":"mental","notes":""},"heal":{"formula":"","healthType":"mental"},"mentalArmor":{"apply":false,"divisor":3,"formula":"1d6"},"status":{"sustaining":false,"pushDuration":0,"pushed":false,"pushStartTime":0,"sustainingOn":[]}},"flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"bC9iPdMedy2c6A2u"}
{"name":"Psi Shield","permission":{"default":0,"qJl17WpEHiovQQBC":3},"type":"sleight","data":{"description":"<p>You rally the mind&rsquo;s defenses against psychic attacks. Increase mental armor by 1d6, +1d6 per superior success.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 285","duration":"sustained","infectionMod":2,"sleightType":"gamma","action":"complex","timeframe":0,"effectsToSelf":[],"effectsToTarget":[],"scaleEffectsOnSuperior":true,"attack":{"useMentalArmor":false,"attackTraits":[],"damageFormula":"","damageType":"mental","notes":""},"heal":{"formula":"","healthType":"mental"},"mentalArmor":{"apply":true,"divisor":3,"formula":"1d6"},"status":{"sustaining":false,"pushDuration":0,"pushed":false,"pushStartTime":0,"sustainingOn":[]}},"flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"eY6KY0jSlNNnwVOp"}
{"name":"Deep Scan","permission":{"default":0,"qJl17WpEHiovQQBC":3},"type":"sleight","data":{"description":"<p>Deep Scan is a more intrusive version of Browse Thoughts ▶283. You telepathically invade the target&rsquo;s mind and probe it for information. You extract two pieces of information (i.e., a name, image, passcode, description or summary a few sentences long, or a memory of less than a minute) plus two for each superior success. Each item takes one full action turn to retrieve, during which the sleight must be sustained.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 283","duration":"sustained","infectionMod":6,"sleightType":"gamma","action":"complex","timeframe":0,"effectsToSelf":[{"type":"misc","unique":"","description":"Retrieve 2 items from target’s mind","id":"dx2r6wl89p"}],"effectsToTarget":[{"type":"misc","unique":"","description":"Your mind is being probed.","id":"nehrd4ik6w"}],"scaleEffectsOnSuperior":true,"attack":{"useMentalArmor":false,"attackTraits":[],"damageFormula":"","damageType":"mental","notes":""},"heal":{"formula":"","healthType":"mental"},"mentalArmor":{"apply":false,"divisor":3,"formula":"1d6"},"status":{"sustaining":false,"pushDuration":0,"pushed":false,"pushStartTime":0,"sustainingOn":[]}},"flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"eZCkKknMnZErzb9Q"}
{"name":"Subliminal","permission":{"default":0,"qJl17WpEHiovQQBC":3},"type":"sleight","data":{"description":"<p>You implant a single post-hypnotic suggestion into the target&rsquo;s mind which they will carry out as if it was their own idea. Implanted suggestions must be short and simple; the GM may require suggestions be encompassed in a short sentence (for example: &ldquo;open the airlock&rdquo; or &ldquo;hand over the weapon&rdquo;). Suggestions may include a short trigger condition (&ldquo;when the alarm goes off, ignore it&rdquo;). The target receives a WIL Check to resist any suggestion that is immediately life threatening (&ldquo;jump off the bridge&rdquo;) or that violates their motivations or personal strictures.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 285","duration":"hours","infectionMod":10,"sleightType":"gamma","action":"complex","timeframe":0,"effectsToSelf":[],"effectsToTarget":[{"type":"misc","unique":"","description":"Implant suggested action in target’s mind that they must carry through.","id":"z4ajww1lke"}],"scaleEffectsOnSuperior":false,"attack":{"useMentalArmor":false,"attackTraits":[],"damageFormula":"","damageType":"mental","notes":""},"heal":{"formula":"","healthType":"mental"},"mentalArmor":{"apply":false,"divisor":3,"formula":"1d6"},"status":{"sustaining":false,"pushDuration":0,"pushed":false,"pushStartTime":0,"sustainingOn":[]}},"flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"fAR2zWZ3e6WcEMP6"}
{"name":"Basilisk Stare","permission":{"default":0,"qJl17WpEHiovQQBC":3},"type":"sleight","data":{"description":"<p>You make eye contact with the target and immobilize them. As long as you keep your gaze locked on them (minor blinking aside), they cannot move, avert their eyes, or undertake any action (including mesh and mental actions). You must also limit your movement, though you may move at half your base move and/or take quick physical actions, but you must make a REF Check to keep your eyes locked, and actions requiring a test and visual coordination suffer a -30 modifier. Likewise, if the target is attacked, moved, or otherwise jostled, eye contact is lost.</p>\n<p>You may not affect extra targets with this sleight, unless you have more than one set of eyes.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 282","duration":"sustained","infectionMod":6,"sleightType":"gamma","action":"task","timeframe":0,"effectsToSelf":[{"type":"misc","unique":"","description":"Target cannot break eye contact with you, both are immobilized.","id":"csosj1euv0"},{"type":"successTest","tags":[{"type":"action","action":"","subtype":""}],"modifier":-30,"toOpponent":false,"requirement":"test needs visual coordination","id":"i6z58cim6b"}],"effectsToTarget":[{"type":"misc","unique":"","description":"You cannot break eye contact with the async, both are immobilized.","id":"1eaicvek3c"}],"scaleEffectsOnSuperior":false,"attack":{"useMentalArmor":false,"attackTraits":[],"damageFormula":"","damageType":"mental","notes":""},"heal":{"formula":"","healthType":"mental"},"mentalArmor":{"apply":false,"divisor":3,"formula":"1d6"},"status":{"sustaining":false,"pushDuration":0,"pushed":false,"pushStartTime":0,"sustainingOn":[]}},"flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"gZdv8mssQwP6284y"}
{"name":"Influence","permission":{"default":0,"qJl17WpEHiovQQBC":3},"type":"sleight","data":{"description":"<p>This is an offensive version of the Control Behavior sleight. You manipulate the target&rsquo;s cortices and emotions. Apply an Enhanced Behavior or Restricted Behavior (Level 2) trait ▶80. You may push this trait to Level 3.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 285","duration":"actionTurns","infectionMod":4,"sleightType":"gamma","action":"complex","timeframe":0,"effectsToSelf":[],"effectsToTarget":[{"type":"misc","unique":"","description":"Apply an Enhanced Behavior or Restricted Behavior (Level 2) trait. Level 3 if pushed","id":"q71cmnro0y"}],"scaleEffectsOnSuperior":false,"attack":{"useMentalArmor":false,"attackTraits":[],"damageFormula":"","damageType":"mental","notes":""},"heal":{"formula":"","healthType":"mental"},"mentalArmor":{"apply":false,"divisor":3,"formula":"1d6"},"status":{"sustaining":false,"pushDuration":0,"pushed":false,"pushStartTime":0,"sustainingOn":[]}},"flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"h6tcRs0G2fGPF995"}
{"name":"Burst of Clarity","permission":{"default":0,"qJl17WpEHiovQQBC":3},"type":"sleight","data":{"description":"<p>You refresh the target&rsquo;s mind, enabling them to see things in a new light. They receive +1 Insight pool for WIL &divide; 5 minutes. A target may only benefit from one burst of clarity at a time.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 283","duration":"minutes","infectionMod":6,"sleightType":"gamma","action":"complex","timeframe":0,"effectsToSelf":[],"effectsToTarget":[{"type":"pool","pool":"insight","modifier":1,"usabilityModification":"","id":"t8qe2vlv4g"}],"scaleEffectsOnSuperior":false,"attack":{"useMentalArmor":false,"attackTraits":[],"damageFormula":"","damageType":"mental","notes":""},"heal":{"formula":"","healthType":"mental"},"mentalArmor":{"apply":false,"divisor":3,"formula":"1d6"},"status":{"sustaining":false,"pushDuration":0,"pushed":false,"pushStartTime":0,"sustainingOn":[]}},"flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"kOlUKl3cItw5JJ8E"}
{"name":"Sense Infection","permission":{"default":0,"qJl17WpEHiovQQBC":3},"type":"sleight","data":{"description":"<p>You detect whether the target is infected with a biological nanovirus or nanoplague strain of the exsurgent virus &mdash; or if they are an async. You know only whether or not the target is infected; superior successes may provide gut feelings about the target&rsquo;s specific strain and its effects.</p>\n<p>GM note: under no circumstances should you provide the name of the strain &mdash; focus on its nature.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 285","duration":"instant","infectionMod":2,"sleightType":"gamma","action":"complex","timeframe":0,"effectsToSelf":[],"effectsToTarget":[{"type":"misc","unique":"","description":"Detect exsurgent infection in biological life.","id":"wogfzn4q31"}],"scaleEffectsOnSuperior":false,"attack":{"useMentalArmor":false,"attackTraits":[],"damageFormula":"","damageType":"mental","notes":""},"heal":{"formula":"","healthType":"mental"},"mentalArmor":{"apply":false,"divisor":3,"formula":"1d6"},"status":{"sustaining":false,"pushDuration":0,"pushed":false,"pushStartTime":0,"sustainingOn":[]}},"flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"lPHW3WBiYfyr4nlh"}
{"name":"Deja Vu","permission":{"default":0,"qJl17WpEHiovQQBC":3},"type":"sleight","data":{"description":"<p>Your force the target&rsquo;s mind into recursive loop. They will repeat their actions from the previous 15-30 seconds (5-10 action turns) for the next WIL &divide; 5 minutes. They will repeat their actions as closely as possible, even if their environment and circumstances change. If someone actively interrupts or restrains the target, or otherwise disrupts the loop, they may make a WIL Check to break out of the loop, ending the sleight.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 283","duration":"minutes","infectionMod":8,"sleightType":"gamma","action":"complex","timeframe":0,"effectsToSelf":[],"effectsToTarget":[{"type":"misc","unique":"","description":"The target is forced to repeat their actions of the past 15-30 seconds.","id":"sqkyxbfxu5"}],"scaleEffectsOnSuperior":false,"attack":{"useMentalArmor":false,"attackTraits":[],"damageFormula":"","damageType":"mental","notes":""},"heal":{"formula":"","healthType":"mental"},"mentalArmor":{"apply":false,"divisor":3,"formula":"1d6"},"status":{"sustaining":false,"pushDuration":0,"pushed":false,"pushStartTime":0,"sustainingOn":[]}},"flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"nCRGjXnPUgR854tv"}
{"name":"Spam","permission":{"default":0,"qJl17WpEHiovQQBC":3},"type":"sleight","data":{"description":"<p>You overload and flood the target&rsquo;s sensory cortices, spamming them with confusing and distracting sensory input. The target is impaired, suffering -10 to all actions, plus an extra -10 per superior success, for WIL &divide; 5 action turns.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 285","duration":"actionTurns","infectionMod":6,"sleightType":"gamma","action":"complex","timeframe":0,"effectsToSelf":[],"effectsToTarget":[{"type":"successTest","tags":[{"type":"action","action":"","subtype":""}],"modifier":-10,"toOpponent":false,"requirement":"","id":"1tjtyos052"},{"type":"misc","unique":"","description":"Overwhelmed by sensory input","id":"yjzspcp5ko"}],"scaleEffectsOnSuperior":true,"attack":{"useMentalArmor":false,"attackTraits":[],"damageFormula":"","damageType":"mental","notes":""},"heal":{"formula":"","healthType":"mental"},"mentalArmor":{"apply":false,"divisor":3,"formula":"1d6"},"status":{"sustaining":false,"pushDuration":0,"pushed":false,"pushStartTime":0,"sustainingOn":[]}},"flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"nrtsQSg6rQX9hTQF"}
{"name":"Downtime","permission":{"default":0,"qJl17WpEHiovQQBC":3},"type":"sleight","data":{"description":"<p>You slip the target&rsquo;s mind into a fugue-state regenerative downtime, to repair their psyche. You must sustain this sleight for 4 hours during which you may take no other complex actions. Downtime cannot be concurrent with a long recharge. This process heals 1d6 stress, +1d6 per superior success. Traumas and disorders are unaffected by this sleight. If interrupted, no stress is healed. For all sensory purposes, you and the target are catatonic during downtime, completely oblivious to the outside world. Only severe disturbances or physical shock (such as being wounded or hit by a shock weapon) will bring you or the target out of it. Any target of this sleight other than yourself must make a WIL Check; if they fail, sometime within the next 24 hours they will be subject to one of your influence effects ▶278.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 284","duration":"sustained","infectionMod":2,"sleightType":"gamma","action":"task","timeframe":14400000,"effectsToSelf":[{"type":"misc","unique":"","description":"You're repairing your target's psyche.","id":"vvhzwdtqbn"}],"effectsToTarget":[{"type":"misc","unique":"","description":"Your psyche is being repaired.","id":"82e28hmvby"}],"scaleEffectsOnSuperior":false,"attack":{"useMentalArmor":false,"attackTraits":[],"damageFormula":"","damageType":"mental","notes":""},"heal":{"formula":"1d6","healthType":"mental"},"mentalArmor":{"apply":false,"divisor":3,"formula":"1d6"},"status":{"sustaining":false,"pushDuration":0,"pushed":false,"pushStartTime":0,"sustainingOn":[]}},"flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"o1jImX8P1wBZQV2O"}
{"name":"Block Skill","permission":{"default":0,"qJl17WpEHiovQQBC":3},"type":"sleight","data":{"description":"<p>You install a temporary block in the target&rsquo;s brain, preventing them from using one specified skill (they may not even default) for WIL &divide; 5 minutes.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 282","duration":"minutes","infectionMod":6,"sleightType":"gamma","action":"complex","timeframe":0,"effectsToSelf":[],"effectsToTarget":[{"type":"misc","unique":"","description":"The target may not use a specified skill.","id":"brrmmwwkfi"}],"scaleEffectsOnSuperior":false,"attack":{"useMentalArmor":false,"attackTraits":[],"damageFormula":"","damageType":"mental","notes":""},"heal":{"formula":"","healthType":"mental"},"mentalArmor":{"apply":false,"divisor":3,"formula":"1d6"},"status":{"sustaining":false,"pushDuration":0,"pushed":false,"pushStartTime":0,"sustainingOn":[]}},"flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"rBkPEaTTnZs4crQV"}
{"name":"Cloud Memory","permission":{"default":0,"qJl17WpEHiovQQBC":3},"type":"sleight","data":{"description":"<p>You temporarily disrupt the target&rsquo;s ability to form long-term memories. The target will retain short-term memories during the duration (WIL &divide; 5 minutes), but will soon (after d6 + 4 action turns) forget anything that occurred while this sleight was in effect.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 283","duration":"minutes","infectionMod":6,"sleightType":"gamma","action":"complex","timeframe":0,"effectsToSelf":[],"effectsToTarget":[{"type":"misc","unique":"","description":"Target retains no long-term memories.","id":"drth0l0uvw"}],"scaleEffectsOnSuperior":false,"attack":{"useMentalArmor":false,"attackTraits":[],"damageFormula":"","damageType":"mental","notes":""},"heal":{"formula":"","healthType":"mental"},"mentalArmor":{"apply":false,"divisor":3,"formula":"1d6"},"status":{"sustaining":false,"pushDuration":0,"pushed":false,"pushStartTime":0,"sustainingOn":[]}},"flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"uuHOs9rpPH9biwSf"}
{"name":"Induce Error","permission":{"default":0,"qJl17WpEHiovQQBC":3},"type":"sleight","data":{"description":"<p>You create a glitch in the target&rsquo;s mind that causes them to unconsciously do something wrong. The target automatically fails a random skill test (chosen by the GM) made in the next WIL &divide; 5 minutes. With a superior success, you may choose which skill will fail the next time it is used (if that skill is not used within the duration, the sleight has no effect) or make the failure a superior failure. This usually manifests as the type of common mistake that even a seasoned professional might make. For example, in combat the target could forget to reload a weapon or alert an ally of a flanking foe. Out of combat, the target might save the wrong file, forget where they left something, mistake someone for someone else, or leave a security door unlocked.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 284","duration":"minutes","infectionMod":6,"sleightType":"gamma","action":"complex","timeframe":0,"effectsToSelf":[],"effectsToTarget":[{"type":"misc","unique":"","description":"The target automatically fails the next test they make using skill chosen by async.","id":"fkr6618sgp"}],"scaleEffectsOnSuperior":false,"attack":{"useMentalArmor":false,"attackTraits":[],"damageFormula":"","damageType":"mental","notes":""},"heal":{"formula":"","healthType":"mental"},"mentalArmor":{"apply":false,"divisor":3,"formula":"1d6"},"status":{"sustaining":false,"pushDuration":0,"pushed":false,"pushStartTime":0,"sustainingOn":[]}},"flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"vxogEEWuwttDnJoT"}
{"name":"Infectious Mind","permission":{"default":0,"qJl17WpEHiovQQBC":3},"type":"sleight","data":{"description":"<p>You share a triggered disorder or active infection influence effect with the target. At the GM&rsquo;s discretion, prolonged exposure may inflict stress damage to the target.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 285","duration":"sustained","infectionMod":4,"sleightType":"gamma","action":"complex","timeframe":0,"effectsToSelf":[{"type":"misc","unique":"","description":"You share a triggered disorder or influence effect with the target.","id":"r2yy7z0lhr"}],"effectsToTarget":[{"type":"misc","unique":"","description":"A triggered disorder or influence effect is being shared with you.","id":"pjz2eix4kz"}],"scaleEffectsOnSuperior":false,"attack":{"useMentalArmor":false,"attackTraits":[],"damageFormula":"","damageType":"mental","notes":""},"heal":{"formula":"","healthType":"mental"},"mentalArmor":{"apply":false,"divisor":3,"formula":"1d6"},"status":{"sustaining":false,"pushDuration":0,"pushed":false,"pushStartTime":0,"sustainingOn":[]}},"flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"wGTnsbUkqTjQKAVI"}
{"name":"Invigorate","permission":{"default":0,"qJl17WpEHiovQQBC":3},"type":"sleight","data":{"description":"<p>You trigger a rush of neurochemical energy in the target. They may expend their next complex action collecting themselves; this counts as a short recharge action ▶35, without needing to expend the full 10 minutes. Note that this sleight does not provide an extra recharge, it simply shortens the time frame.</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 285","duration":"instant","infectionMod":4,"sleightType":"gamma","action":"complex","timeframe":0,"effectsToSelf":[],"effectsToTarget":[{"type":"misc","unique":"","description":"The target can expend their next complex action as a short recharge.","id":"i1zt5dzie7"}],"scaleEffectsOnSuperior":false,"attack":{"useMentalArmor":false,"attackTraits":[],"damageFormula":"","damageType":"mental","notes":""},"heal":{"formula":"","healthType":"mental"},"mentalArmor":{"apply":false,"divisor":3,"formula":"1d6"},"status":{"sustaining":false,"pushDuration":0,"pushed":false,"pushStartTime":0,"sustainingOn":[]}},"flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"wzkQSk6zpI6YJdO5"}
